## Title: EpogArmory
## Notes: Made by Defcon. Mesh-based gear inspector. Every client scans groupmates in dungeons/raids, broadcasts gear via addon messages, and stores received broadcasts in EpogArmoryDB for manual upload to epoglogs.com.
